window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As summer descends upon the Blackwood estate, peculiar occurrences cast an eerie shadow over the once peaceful land. Mysterious lights flicker amid the dense woods, leaving an unsettling feeling in the air.</p> <p>Amid the oddness, Asher finds himself consumed by overseeing the estate's expansion, managing crops, and constructing new buildings. With little time for anything else, he tries to push aside the unsettling events taking place in the nearby forests.</p> <p>However, as the shadows encroach closer to Blackwood, Asher and his growing family can no longer ignore the hidden mysteries lurking beneath the surface. While attending to their newfound desires and inexplicable urges, they must confront these enigmatic forces.</p> <p>With their beloved estate hanging in the balance, Blackwood faces its greatest challenge yet. Can Asher and his family withstand the onslaught of new threats, or will the very foundation of Blackwood crumble into dust?</p> <p><i>Blackwood Milk Farm </i>is for mature listeners. It includes mystery, intrigue, slice of life, and unconventional relationships.</p>"; 
